/blockquote><br />\n同埋唔使飲咁多，bodybuilder 都係攝取體重（lb) 咁多既protein, 即係話hardcore 既飲140g 左右，你一日仲會食肉嗰啲，飲咁多腎虧呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/22.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"589785d5a128e2613fb6a3036653b1afc29f4519","tid":143773,"uid":47241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-05T03:57:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>做gym 前一晚24g, gym 當日24g, gym 後嗰日24g, 一星期做兩至三日gym<br />\n<br />\n一日三杯點飲架<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，一杯已經好想嘔 (嘔左就黎一年） <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n嘔左咁耐可能身體唔太適合 轉一轉飲法好wo巴打"},{"pid":"2b6dfc96184e131f109e6d6097d32eeb46cde8f4","tid":143773,"uid":42293,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-05T03:59:54.000Z","msg":"早、午、晚、消夜、夜晚黑扎醒各一杯，咁樣飲係最基本<br />\n如果飲唔夠不如唔好飲，唔係咁樣飲嘅話同冇飲冇分別"},{"pid":"bb791ba8e293ef33913038bc95fa151ce42825d7","tid":143773,"uid":11977,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-05T04:08:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>早、午、晚、消夜、夜晚黑扎醒各一杯，咁樣飲係最基本<br />\n如果飲唔夠不如唔好飲，唔係咁樣飲嘅話同冇飲冇分別</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d78cf6ba9737ff0c1c79a74170a9c09c3d8c38b","tid":143773,"uid":19004,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-05T04:13:02.000Z","msg":"操腎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"78f9df19042eadf6d11a881beabdf818ed1aa91e","tid":143773,"uid":25055,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-05T04:13:16.000Z","msg":"小心柯蛋白尿"},{"pid":"349eac4d1dc84e3a3996de26929698687f6ce041","tid":143773,"uid":38017,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-05T04:31:48.000Z","msg":"gym後飲一杯我覺得已經夠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea7925f8f33c5b1fbaf4fc15db3b7beb61053902","tid":143773,"uid":36291,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-05T04:40:04.000Z","msg":"巴打飲太多啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一日飲幾杯視乎你當日吸收營養既份量<br />\n同埋要飲多d水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />你再咁飲好快虧"},{"pid":"186a45e2d6450e57463fed160472f6abeb3525f3","tid":143773,"uid":32314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-05T05:59:01.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2f99c583713ca3723f0bd8670497de467e9d92c0","tid":143773,"uid":52215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-05T06:11:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>尿有泡就飲小d啦<br />\n介緊</blockquote><br />\n暫時未有泡，聽左樓上咁多巴打講<br />\n都係做gym日最多兩杯，唔做gym一杯算數"},{"pid":"afdf9fa5c3e7c1e766ac683b36d6d784676f61f8","tid":143773,"uid":25468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-05T06:12:56.000Z","msg":"只會 gym 後一scoop <br />\n<br />\n平時增肌 1kg體重飲 1g 已經夠 , cutting 先會需要到 1kg / 2g<br />\n<br />\n唔好靠 whey 做主要吸收 protein 來源"},{"pid":"35f188b257b9c2d4c439ee11ab3b696df432f310","tid":143773,"uid":1255,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-05T10:44:05.000Z","msg":"之前我一日四杯<br />\n訓醒一杯 <br />\n午後一杯<br />\nGym前後各一杯<br />\n<br />\n而家直頭唔撚飲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e097a07028670c64f1b5836375c2226e2d330ebd","tid":143773,"uid":57322,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-05T11:44:40.000Z","msg":"小弟 80kg 一日會食大約200g protein 當中有50g 來自whey"},{"pid":"e1fa6631dc97ff203123d108c6197c9082e7f6cd","tid":143773,"uid":2093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-05T11:48:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>小弟 80kg 一日會食大約200g protein 當中有50g 來自whey</blockquote><br />\n另外150g食d咩？"},{"pid":"cc075f620a920b07c7296b77ea91fb8600223c1b","tid":143773,"uid":38017,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-05T12:05:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>小弟 80kg 一日會食大約200g protein 當中有50g 來自whey</blockquote><br />\n你個名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"29d376b1ecfd0b8fa7fca3ef4c3bc067e7eba79f","tid":143773,"uid":52215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-05T12:53:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>小弟 80kg 一日會食大約200g protein 當中有50g 來自whey</blockquote><br />\n你個名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8163314499db7c5eb523072deac8c60a9dddd449","tid":143773,"uid":22313,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-05T12:53:16.000Z","msg":"操後一次，臨瞓一次都差唔多，你仲有平時正餐會食，唔好完全依賴飲whey嚟吸收protein, whey始終只係supplement，基本上如果你正餐食足同食得啱既話連whey都唔使飲"},{"pid":"73c43b64cd2b10fa889ddcbae168b11ad3741b25","tid":143773,"uid":36291,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-05T12:57:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>小弟 80kg 一日會食大約200g protein 當中有50g 來自whey</blockquote><br />\n巴打小心d好wo"},{"pid":"787f2938180df70aafa48c1ba2395d762d006f5d","tid":143773,"uid":25468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-05T13:48:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>小弟 80kg 一日會食大約200g protein 當中有50g 來自whey</blockquote><br />\n你個名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n身體唔可以一次過分解大量蛋白質 , 你咁款要分8- 10餐去食喎 , 唔洗瞓 ?"},{"pid":"1281d26a4e3ad976c7c366e16bae8c5634949e56","tid":143773,"uid":57322,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T00:16:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>小弟 80kg 一日會食大約200g protein 當中有50g 來自whey</blockquote><br />\n你個名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n身體唔可以一次過分解大量蛋白質 , 你咁款要分8- 10餐去食喎 , 唔洗瞓 ?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我而家用緊intermittent fasting 修緊身 一日只食兩餐 兩個禮拜瘦左7-8lb 腹肌都出返黎 其實已經有research證明左一日一餐同一日六餐個成效差唔多"},{"pid":"9f80400d136222b0d2e5694ea39a1d01ae1f4a7a","tid":143773,"uid":57322,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T00:17:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>小弟 80kg 一日會食大約200g protein 當中有50g 來自whey</blockquote><br />\n另外150g食d咩？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n雞柳 蛋 飯 西蘭花 雜菜 燕麥"},{"pid":"765871b8834a7bd9cbaeb687667147c672ad1aca","tid":143773,"uid":34939,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T00:20:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>早、午、晚、消夜、夜晚黑扎醒各一杯，咁樣飲係最基本<br />\n如果飲唔夠不如唔好飲，唔係咁樣飲嘅話同冇飲冇分別</blockquote><br />\n當水飲先係基本 即係八杯<br />\n你一日先得嗰五杯點會叫基本<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ecca66f5d4373a63effc4a7e07914c3241574160","tid":143773,"uid":51932,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T00:20:21.000Z","msg":"訓前係飲casein㗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c3d76685e3fe2077783c9fe1297e6a047e9dbdf8","tid":143773,"uid":51594,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T00:21:26.000Z","msg":"驚頂唔順可以不一匙就喺台面，之後捲起張銀紙係咁索<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dcbce71f79660ae9bdb695f896991605a0045a42","tid":143773,"uid":57322,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T00:21:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>小弟 80kg 一日會食大約200g protein 當中有50g 來自whey</blockquote><br />\n巴打小心d好wo</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有research講過人體就算食到 4.5g/kg 既protein都未有明顯大問題 當然又唔洗食咁多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我一星期操5-6日 食2.5g/kg 我覺得唔過份"},{"pid":"33fef6a5b3f426b30fc8d9208d5dc2d5c2ae5650","tid":143773,"uid":57322,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T00:23:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"http://www.mysupplementmart.com/media/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/o/n/on-100-whey-gold-standard-chocolate-mint-5lbs.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.mysupplementmart.com%2Fmedia%2Fcatalog%2Fproduct%2Fcache%2F1%2Fimage%2F9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95%2Fo%2Fn%2Fon-100-whey-gold-standard-chocolate-mint-5lbs.jpg&h=9daad417&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n我體重65 kg, 呢隻on whey一匙24克蛋白， 一日我飲三杯，gym前及後各一杯，訓前一杯<br />\n我想問唔做gym個日，唔飲會唔會冇咁好？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔做應該都要飲，因為你身體要recover 不過都要睇你食得夠唔夠 最好都係食真正既食物"},{"pid":"1daaf021edeea5202faeff3b8199ef7404f87c70","tid":143773,"uid":84415,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T00:38:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>驚頂唔順可以不一匙就喺台面，之後捲起張銀紙係咁索<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b011519d7d87c1896acbdd76250d5253267067a9","tid":143773,"uid":31834,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T00:40:22.000Z","msg":"午餐同晚餐中間飲一杯，晚上做完飲一杯"},{"pid":"c47ba02ab4a4a541ec1f72aee79aea6328c2aa52","tid":143773,"uid":47523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T00:49:39.000Z","msg":"都係個句，正餐一定好過whey，whey半個鐘頭乜都冇晒，正餐就推持到三四個鐘<br />\n<br />\n而腎虧，係睇你整個飲食習慣同需求，如果一個人常飲水同堅操，係唔存在肝腎問題，不過差唔多所有新手都係未識操又尻食，但講到飲粉就成個專家咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，呢啲已經懶得點醒佢，轉頭練到非洲兒童咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"baae429dbd63a1904209304d7afecc78e15d6065","tid":143773,"uid":25468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T00:49:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>小弟 80kg 一日會食大約200g protein 當中有50g 來自whey</blockquote><br />\n你個名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n身體唔可以一次過分解大量蛋白質 , 你咁款要分8- 10餐去食喎 , 唔洗瞓 ?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我而家用緊intermittent fasting 修緊身 一日只食兩餐 兩個禮拜瘦左7-8lb 腹肌都出返黎 其實已經有research證明左一日一餐同一日六餐個成效差唔多</blockquote><br />\n俾個 source 睇下得唔得？"},{"pid":"4cfbe45b22fef8eeeaab85078d1b295d4c043576","tid":143773,"uid":47523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T00:52:02.000Z","msg":"同埋唔記得講，大部分人飲whey係唔溝碳水，真心唔明班柒頭諗咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"86a2a77ec2c5a3c678653c9b3f4f1c831fdb51e7","tid":143773,"uid":25468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T00:58:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>同埋唔記得講，大部分人飲whey係唔溝碳水，真心唔明班柒頭諗咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有人教人空肚飲都有啦，唔溝碳水飲有幾奇"},{"pid":"10a8ec61bc1357d7d90459d809b4c39e812bb5e0","tid":143773,"uid":25794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T01:05:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>驚頂唔順可以不一匙就喺台面，之後捲起張銀紙係咁索<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"41e80dc6f1634bcdefed045f4e402fac279be537","tid":143773,"uid":1255,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T01:15:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>同埋唔記得講，大部分人飲whey係唔溝碳水，真心唔明班柒頭諗咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有人教人空肚飲都有啦，唔溝碳水飲有幾奇</blockquote><br />\n溝唔溝要睇個人<br />\n條友係肥+壯要乾番身仲要溝碳水？<br />\n十隻手指都有長短啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7edae082795c189a34570ad81905a61e62ab471b","tid":143773,"uid":57322,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T01:25:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>小弟 80kg 一日會食大約200g protein 當中有50g 來自whey</blockquote><br />\n你個名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n身體唔可以一次過分解大量蛋白質 , 你咁款要分8- 10餐去食喎 , 唔洗瞓 ?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我而家用緊intermittent fasting 修緊身 一日只食兩餐 兩個禮拜瘦左7-8lb 腹肌都出返黎 其實已經有research證明左一日一餐同一日六餐個成效差唔多</blockquote><br />\n俾個 source 睇下得唔得？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.crossfitinvictus.com/blog/does-eating-six-meals-a-day-really-increase-your-metabolism/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.crossfitinvictus.com%2Fblog%2Fdoes-eating-six-meals-a-day-really-increase-your-metabolism%2F&d=Zo4i0ptUI%2BsV2bg8TrofrLIOlR6kLHi1VdsYCD5DrTY%3D&h=e703cc22\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.crossfitinvictus.com/blog/does-eating-six-meals-a-day-really-increase-your-metabolism/</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://one-minutefitness.blogspot.hk/2016/07/protein-limit.html?m=1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fone-minutefitness.blogspot.hk%2F2016%2F07%2Fprotein-limit.html%3Fm%3D1&d=Zo4i0ptUI%2BsV2bg8TrofrLIOlR6kLHi1VdsYCD5DrTY%3D&h=06839957\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://one-minutefitness.blogspot.hk/2016/07/protein-limit.html?m=1</a>"},{"pid":"aecf2b7d16970a853623944ee1e1e0bd08240e84","tid":143773,"uid":20302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T01:28:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>同埋唔記得講，大部分人飲whey係唔溝碳水，真心唔明班柒頭諗咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有人教人空肚飲都有啦，唔溝碳水飲有幾奇</blockquote><br />\n溝唔溝要睇個人<br />\n條友係肥+壯要乾番身仲要溝碳水？<br />\n十隻手指都有長短啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔溝碳水就係柒頭？正餐都食唔少啦 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ecb211ece54123ed2f7f325876edc1ba1756880c","tid":143773,"uid":25468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T01:33:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>小弟 80kg 一日會食大約200g protein 當中有50g 來自whey</blockquote><br />\n你個名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n身體唔可以一次過分解大量蛋白質 , 你咁款要分8- 10餐去食喎 , 唔洗瞓 ?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我而家用緊intermittent fasting 修緊身 一日只食兩餐 兩個禮拜瘦左7-8lb 腹肌都出返黎 其實已經有research證明左一日一餐同一日六餐個成效差唔多</blockquote><br />\n俾個 source 睇下得唔得？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.crossfitinvictus.com/blog/does-eating-six-meals-a-day-really-increase-your-metabolism/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.crossfitinvictus.com%2Fblog%2Fdoes-eating-six-meals-a-day-really-increase-your-metabolism%2F&d=Zo4i0ptUI%2BsV2bg8TrofrLIOlR6kLHi1VdsYCD5DrTY%3D&h=e703cc22\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.crossfitinvictus.com/blog/does-eating-six-meals-a-day-really-increase-your-metabolism/</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://one-minutefitness.blogspot.hk/2016/07/protein-limit.html?m=1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fone-minutefitness.blogspot.hk%2F2016%2F07%2Fprotein-limit.html%3Fm%3D1&d=Zo4i0ptUI%2BsV2bg8TrofrLIOlR6kLHi1VdsYCD5DrTY%3D&h=06839957\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://one-minutefitness.blogspot.hk/2016/07/protein-limit.html?m=1</a></blockquote><br />\nthx <br />\n不過你既然cutting 緊，實體食物先係蛋白質吸收來源，你飲果50g whey 唔認為你會吸收到囉"},{"pid":"03e21d2e395d5839501d195f1bf1d0338b921657","tid":143773,"uid":77730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T01:35:53.000Z","msg":"因為窮一日二次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 每日要150g蛋白<br />\n冇操都照飲"},{"pid":"4666d106df182ffcda768597d32aed8bfbf2dc83","tid":143773,"uid":57322,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T03:06:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>小弟 80kg 一日會食大約200g protein 當中有50g 來自whey</blockquote><br />\n你個名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n身體唔可以一次過分解大量蛋白質 , 你咁款要分8- 10餐去食喎 , 唔洗瞓 ?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我而家用緊intermittent fasting 修緊身 一日只食兩餐 兩個禮拜瘦左7-8lb 腹肌都出返黎 其實已經有research證明左一日一餐同一日六餐個成效差唔多</blockquote><br />\n俾個 source 睇下得唔得？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.crossfitinvictus.com/blog/does-eating-six-meals-a-day-really-increase-your-metabolism/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.crossfitinvictus.com%2Fblog%2Fdoes-eating-six-meals-a-day-really-increase-your-metabolism%2F&d=Zo4i0ptUI%2BsV2bg8TrofrLIOlR6kLHi1VdsYCD5DrTY%3D&h=e703cc22\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.crossfitinvictus.com/blog/does-eating-six-meals-a-day-really-increase-your-metabolism/</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://one-minutefitness.blogspot.hk/2016/07/protein-limit.html?m=1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fone-minutefitness.blogspot.hk%2F2016%2F07%2Fprotein-limit.html%3Fm%3D1&d=Zo4i0ptUI%2BsV2bg8TrofrLIOlR6kLHi1VdsYCD5DrTY%3D&h=06839957\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://one-minutefitness.blogspot.hk/2016/07/protein-limit.html?m=1</a></blockquote><br />\nthx <br />\n不過你既然cutting 緊，實體食物先係蛋白質吸收來源，你飲果50g whey 唔認為你會吸收到囉</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我都係格堅食夠個份量<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}